        "notes": "Nationals not on the 88-country visa-free exemption list (and not from Bangladesh, Nepal, Nigeria, Pakistan, Sri Lanka, Vietnam) may apply for an 'Entry Permit' (Authorization to Enter and Stay, aka visa-upon-arrival) at any border checkpoint Visa Room upon arrival. Fee: MOP200 single / MOP300 multiple for individuals; MOP400/MOP600 for family passports; MOP100/MOP150 for children under 12; MOP100/MOP150 for groups of 10+ with collective travel document. Officials of diplomatic missions of Bangladesh, Nepal, Nigeria, Pakistan, Sri Lanka, and Vietnam holding diplomatic/consular identification may also apply for visa-upon-arrival.",
